# build/QA evidence — HQ-side artifacts, never part of the commons itself
.build-evidence-*.md

# dashboard emit artifacts — HQ-side observatory records, not part of the commons
dashboard-record-*.json

# local editor state — not part of the commons
.obsidian/

# runtime residue — not part of the commons
.omc/
.omx/

# Meep runtime raw-capture — never committed to this public repo.
